<div class="container">
            <h1>Why it's important to treat hearing loss early</h1>
            <p>Treating hearing loss early can make all the difference in the world, allowing you to rediscover parts of your life that may have felt missing.</p>
            <ul>
                <li>
                    <img src="${URLUtils.staticURL('/images/shoe.png')}" alt="Exercise shoe" />
                    <h2>Enjoy your daily activities again</h2>
                    <p>Whether it's gardening or going to the gym, better hearing can help you be more involved in your everyday activities.</p>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <img src="${URLUtils.staticURL('/images/heart-hands.png')}" alt="Heart" />
                    <h2>Stay connected to the people you love</h2>
                    <p>Reengaging in conversations with family and friends can help you feel more connected to important relationships.</p>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <img src="${URLUtils.staticURL('/images/lightbulb.png')}" alt="Light bulb" />
                    <h2>Discover more independence</h2>
                    <p>When you're more aware of your surroundings, you'll be able to do more without having to rely on anyone else.</p>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <img src="${URLUtils.staticURL('/images/brain.png')}" alt="Brain" />
                    <h2>Support brain health</h2>
                    <p>Reduce the risk of cognitive decline and diseases such as Alzheimer's or dementia.</p>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>

